<tr id="L130"><td><a href="#L130">130</a></td><td>JAMESON:  The herb and drug combinations are self-administered slowly over a period of two years. Every response is different, depending on a being's DNA. I got enough for both of us, Annie, but I had to test it on myself first. I couldn't risk you. If I died, well, I was half a man, so what did it matter.</td></tr>

