<tr id="L132"><td><a href="#L132">132</a></td><td>JAMESON:  But I was starting to change, Anne. It was almost undetectable, but the improvement was there. Then when this hostage situation came up, I knew I'd have to be at my peak to deal with it. I didn't have time to wait for the drug to work naturally.</td></tr>

